{"tid":1089371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想你了...","createTime":"2019-04-02T17:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T21:11:26.000Z","uid":123911,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39b96a079de35f4146b17c3d9054a21358065aa7","tid":1089371,"uid":123911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"愛情，或許就是在他面前，心會漏拍，臉紅耳赤，深怕心跳聲大得對方都能聽見。很想有下一步卻又害怕。每日每夜都想著他，就連夢裡都是他，想他正在幹嘛，想他有沒有想我。即使在茫茫人海之中，你眼中就只有他。<br />\n他的每個言行舉止，即使時間久了，也不會忘記，好像他就成為了你生活中的一部分，想分也分不開。<br />\n你認定他就是那個命中注定的一位，唯一一位，沒有人能夠取代他，沒有了他的你，感覺便是人生少了一部分的自己；沒有了他的你，生命是不完整的。<br />\n你不會再介意所謂的世俗眼光，即使他並沒有符合到你原本的擇偶條件，你的心卻牢牢的鎖定了他。<br />\n或許，這就是愛情。可惜，我錯過了愛情，卻留下了對你的憶記。"},{"pid":"1ac77d7c53cee71de67e3d783f837f566208d40f","tid":1089371,"uid":123911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"我好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔知佢有冇掛住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d16079addcf98d7caa49b8f19c439722ff2c6a2","tid":1089371,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ac77d7c53cee71de67e3d783f837f566208d40f","tid":1089371,"uid":123911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"我好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔知佢有冇掛住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:46:49.000Z","msg":"無啦"},{"pid":"e0d463039f429a597ed11f41578c513e6f98e3c6","tid":1089371,"uid":123911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d16079addcf98d7caa49b8f19c439722ff2c6a2","tid":1089371,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ac77d7c53cee71de67e3d783f837f566208d40f","tid":1089371,"uid":123911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"我好